  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we settled down there, I suddenly started to cry, you know, because I was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was probably my first experience with being between illusion and reality, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was still a little kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and one time I went there when I was already order.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we usually went all together, my father, my mother, and my sister and I, on vacations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in that year for some reason my father and sister didn't go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I went alone with my mother to that town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember we had a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We hiked in the forest there and, and it was my first experience, I think, in-- with, with great art in Wurzburg, the, the next big town, a bigger town, big town, Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is a palace of, of a bishop and beautiful murals or paintings on the ceilings by a famous Italian master, Tiepolo.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was so impressed by it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was really the first time that I saw something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so when-- when we came home after the summer vacations, we always got-- we had to write essays about our vacation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I wrote about that essay-- I wrote about that experience, about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got a real-- I got an E on that essay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and I remember that vacation very well with my mother alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] altogether I was-- I loved my mother very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think she loved me, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so-- but any more details I really can't recall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] You know, about essays, writing in school, this is one interesting story.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
